PrecisAcceptance of a DESIGNATION wherein the POUNDMAKER BAND surrenders, for an indefinite term, all of its rights and interests in and to the oil and gas that may exist within, upon or under certain of its reserve lands in Saskatchewan, for the purpose of allowing the Crown to issue leases, etc., to third parties for oil and gas exploration and development.
